      • DepthFirstIterator

        public DepthFirstIterator(Tree<V,E> tree)
        Create the iterator over a tree. The tree is read and the vertices arranged (internally) so that they can be read back one at a time in a depth-first order.
        Parameters:
        tree - the tree to which to attach the iterator.
